<br>
Take your choice.  (ooc: providing no work/school on that day ill be in Akanon for this event. ).  <br>
<br>
Friend : The dwarf glances at you , grins with a confident half hearted smile that makes you feel assured of the safty of the city.  You continue to pass, heartbeat slowing from the panic you felt, now to a calm.  You just want to pass out from the experience.<br>
<br>
Foe : From the glance you feel a urge in your being to flee.  As you proceed the glance turns into a stare which then turns into a bit more interest than you were really hopeing for.  Standing away from the wall and straght he drops the head to the ground and unsheeths the glowing red sword and then another one with less aura but equaly intimidating.  You find youself in a duel to the death! <br>
<br>
